Privacy Policy / Terms of Service

American Digital Services is an information technology firm located in upstate NY that focuses on web application programming and web hosting services. We provide Web Development and Managed CMS (for Wordpress, Joomla, and Drupal), Managed Server Security (for Linux and Windows), Custom Development (PHP), PCI Compliance Services, Social Marketing, Organic SEO, Disaster Recovery Planning, Computer Support (Remote and On-Site), CTO Support. We are your source for Email Security Services (Mailprotector), Cloud Services (Google Apps, Office 365, Backup Services and more), Web Hosting (on Private Cloud, Virtual Servers, and Dedicated Hardware), Managed Hosting (on Virtual Servers and Dedicated Hardware), SSL Certificates, Hosted and Managed CRM. American Digital Services "Where you are only limited by imagination"

American Digital Services is an equal opportunity employer who hires based on your skills, desire to work, and attitude toward others. We do not allow race, color, religion, sex, national origin, genetics, disability, and/or age to be a deciding factor in employment with us.
